And you will probably need to desactivate your network device before to macchange it :

So, as root :

* ifconfig *eth0* down (assuming your network device is eth0)
* macchanger -a *eth0*
* ifconfig *eth0* up

**Before**, you should have a look to this :

<https://tails.boum.org/forum/macchanger/> and 
<https://tails.boum.org/todo/macchanger>


-- bulo

